<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(270deg, #54A7DA 0.43%, #123D64 66.21%);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        .email-header img {
            width: 75%;
            max-width: 480px;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
            border: 1px solid #FBBF32;
            color: #123d64 !important;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 10rem;
            background: #FBBF32;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="https://my.fearfree.com/sfsites/c/cms/delivery/media/MCCEXC4KMBVRG4ZJVQZZQZOSAQAQ?version=1.1&channelId=0apTR000000039B&width=640" alt="Fear Free Banner">
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello {!Receiving_User.FirstName},</p>

            <p>
               An account already exists under this email address. To reset your password, click the button below:
            </p>

            <p>
                <a href="{!Community_Url}" target="_blank" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
            </p>

            <p>
                If you have any issues resetting your password, please reach out to <a href="mailto:wags@fearfree.com">wags@fearfree.com</a> for assistance.
            </p>

            <p>For the love of animals,<br>The Fear Free Team</p>

            <div class="footer">
                This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>